│ (`-print-all-alias-modref-info`) output. It shows that `BasicAA` reports `NoModRef`     │
│ between the two calls to `llvm.dx.resource.handlefrombinding`. This is the critical     │
│ piece of incorrect information feeding into GVN.                                        │
│                                                                                         │
│ ```                                                                                     │
