│ modify `BasicAAResult::getModRefBehavior` to recognize                                  │
│ `llvm.dx.resource.handlefrombinding` and return a conservative `ModRef` result,         │
│ indicating that it might read or write memory. This will prevent GVN and other          │
│ optimizations from incorrectly reordering or eliminating these calls.                   │
│                                                                                         │
│ **File**: `llvm/lib/Analysis/BasicAliasAnalysis.cpp`                                    │
