│   %bufExit = tail call target("dx.RawBuffer", i32, 1, 0)                                │
│ @llvm.dx.resource.handlefrombinding(i32 0, i32 0, i32 4, i32 %loadGlobal, ptr nonnull   │
│ @Out.str)                                                                               │
